Package: stormwindmodel
Type: Package
Title: Model Tropical Cyclone Wind Speeds
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2016-10-21
Author: G. Brooke Anderson,
    Andrea Schumacher (andrea.schumacher@colostate.edu),
    Seth Guikema,
    Joshua M. Ferreri,
    Steven Quiring
Maintainer: G. Brooke Anderson <brooke.anderson@colostate.edu>
Description: This package allows you to input tracking data for a hurricane
    or other tropical storm, along with a data frame of grid points at which
    to model wind speeds, and functions in this package will calculate wind
    speeds at each point based on wind model equations. This work was supported
    in part by grants from the National Institute of Environmental Health
    Sciences (R00ES022631) and the National Science Foundation (1331399).
URL: https://github.com/geanders/stormwindmodel
BugReports: https://github.com/geanders/stormwindmodel/issues
License: GPL-2
